[build]
  functions = "netlify/functions"

[functions]
  node_bundler = "esbuild"

# Optional: redirect /track to the function for a cleaner URL
[[redirects]]
  from   = "/track"
  to     = "/.netlify/functions/track"
  status = 200

# SimpleObjectz — Delhivery Tracking Proxy

Netlify serverless function that proxies Delhivery API calls to fix browser CORS restrictions.

## Files
- `netlify/functions/track.js` — the proxy function
- `netlify.toml` — Netlify build config

## Deploy Steps (5 minutes)

1. Go to https://github.com and create a new repository named `simpleobjectz-tracker`
2. Upload these files (drag and drop on GitHub)
3. Go to https://app.netlify.com → Add new site → Import from GitHub
4. Select the repo → Deploy site
5. Copy your Netlify URL (e.g. `https://simpleobjectz-tracker.netlify.app`)
6. Paste it into order-tracking.html (see PROXY_BASE line)

## Endpoint

GET `/.netlify/functions/track?awb=1234567890`
GET `/.netlify/functions/track?order_id=1110001`
